Homepage: https://github.com/spectrum-redteamer/spectrum-project
Description: Autonomous Cyber Reasoning System
 Spectrum is an autonomous "Cyber Reasoning System" (CRS) that utilizes
 Large Language Models (DeepSeek-V4 and Qwen families) to perform
 high-level planning, exploitation, and remediation.
